You can simply ask Alexa to control your lock. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our “Turbolock Plus” app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our “Turbolock Plus” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Enable “Turbolock” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Turbolock” login page;
(4) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(5) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, lock my front door.”
“Alexa, unlock the back door.”
“Alexa, is front door locked?”
